attribute_definition: ID number associated with water system in the supplier service area. eAR data are reported by PWSID.

DWR assigned ID number associated with the urban retail water supplier. We used the publically available PWSID/DWR_ORG_ID crosswalk to map the DWR_ORG_ID to the PWSID. Note that there are many cases where there is no DWR_ORG_ID for a given PWSID.
Calendar year associated with the number of sources.

The category of source water. Levels = c("emergency interties", "groundwater", "purchased grounwater", 
"purchased surface water", "standby sources", "surface water")
The status of source water. Levels = c("approved", "new")
